<L>__{ext day: corleone street}
<A>__{michael and his bodyguards move through the empty streets of the village. they walk behind him, and spread to either side about fifteen feet away from him. they move down ancient steps, past an old stone fountain. michael hesitates, cups his hands and drinks some water. they go on. they move up a very narrow old street. michael looks at the doorways that they pass. moving view: each door has a plaque, with a ribbon or flower. calo sees michael looking.}
